Me ŋgomte lɛ ben ekumyì mwɛɛm mvù bonyii bo ntum Nyo' le bò yuule to jemyɛɛ lɛ mvú nu ke ekooy, ebvuu ekumyì tɛn mwɛɛm mvù boom bo ntum e bo Jisos e to jemyɛɛ ɛ̂ ben lɛ Tata bô Mboyse nu ɛ gay lɛ ben egeè.
Wee wvù duu lɛ wen kee Nyo', geenɛn yaa gɛɛle bonci bew kɛ, nu wee mbiay, ɛ kecɛɛy yaa nu yî ye le kɛ.
Ben kee lo lɛ Klistu to to keecake bibefɛ bi bonyii le. Ɛ kɛ wvú wvù Klistu to kɛŋke kebefɛ kɛ.
Nsáa yɛm shém, no Nyo' to koŋɛɛ beene ɛ̂ yin je le nɛn, beene tɛn kɛŋke keekoŋenè.
Beene kee lo tɛn lɛ beene nu bonyii bo Nyo' le, ɛ bonyii bò ɛ̀ nu bo yî woŋ wvun e bocii nu can wee kebefɛ wɛ le.
Nyɛkeey enù fô wo le. Nsáa yesebeewo gayte wo le. Gayɛ nsáa yesebeewo le yicii wee mwaaŋ mwaaŋ bó le, enya ɛ̂ me.
noo fô Jisos Klistu wvù ɛ̀ nu kɛ wvú wvù ké no duŋci fiɛɛ fi kecɛɛy ɛkumɛ Nyo' ɛ̂ bonyii le. Ɛ̀ to nu wvú wee wvu fwe keekase buy yî kpwe le. Ɛ ɛ̀ nu wvú wvù saake bonfon bocii bo yî nshɛ le fɛn. Mbense enù fô wvú le. Ɛ̀ nu wvú wvù kooŋke beene, ɛ wvú to bvuse beene can kebefɛ kesɛɛbeene le bô ɛlɛmɛ kew.
Ɛ ɛ̀ nu kɛ lɛŋlɛŋ no ben kɛŋke tɛn bonyii bomew ŋgoo yene le bò bii n'yɛɛyi bonyii bo Nikolaus e.
Nonɛn, no ben nu kɛ lo finɛn ɛntelɛŋ yaa lɛɛ kɛnɛɛ yvuwse, me nu ŋke encuy ben ɛ̂ me ɛmvu.
Ɛ me mbee kpwe baay lɛ wee to baa nu dvú wvù nu ɛ kocɛn wvù nulo eyene ŋwa' wvudvu kɛnɛɛ taa ɛnte jodvu kɛ.
Ɛ Waa Njee ke bay kelay ke bokaŋ botɛte, ɛ me n'yuw ɛ fiɛɛ fi bokaŋ botɛte ŋgoo mwɛɛm mvu mvuyuum mwɛ le gay lɛ, “To!” Lɛ me ntaa, nɛ n'yɛn nyambala mi yì yiile le, ɛ wee ɛ ben yî dvú le kɛŋke nfew wvù bó feeke mwɛɛm yî dvú le ɛ̂ wvú ɛbo.
Ɛ Waa Njee ke bay kelay ke bokaŋ bosooshwiy yî ŋwa' wɛ le, ɛ mondvuum cife fowe nɛn ndvumm gɛn buy keŋgawtɛn ke ntam kefew e.
Mwɛɛm mvu boŋgɛw e mvun mvù ɛ̀ to nu, ŋguy bô njiim noo fiɛɛ diɛwɛ mvuŋkaŋ mvù bɛɛnci le, mvù to buyte ɛ̂ nyámbala yidvu ɛmvu to nu ɛ yu bonyii keba kemwaaŋ ɛnte jo bitɛte.
Ɛ bocɛ' bo bonyii le bo mbaanfiɛɛ ncow bonɛw ba bò shiilɛɛ yî bokawla bobole fwe dvu Nyo' mum no gbwee tumte monshim mobole fokuse, nyaa mbense wvu baay ɛ̂ Nyo'.
ɛ bonyii bocii bò nu fó, laŋlaŋè tɛn.
Ɛ me n'yuw ɛ diɛw too fowe yole diɛwɛ joo yì gbwee ɛ̂ ŋkoŋ e, dvûmte tɛn diɛwɛ jaŋ yì baykene le. Diɛw yì me n'yuwɛɛ yidvu to jemyi tɛn diɛwɛ dikome fò bonyii kumte le.
Ɛjim jodvu ɛ me nɛ ntaa, n'yɛn ɛ bó yene yew ncese yi fowe yì ɛ̀ nu cun yì duŋci lɛ Nyo' nu bô bonyii.
Ɛ kelaante ke baay sɛnɛn buy biba bitɛte. Ɛ bilaante bi bitum e no keeshi. Nyo' to nu ɛ kume kelaante ke baay kin kè ɛ̀ nu Babilon, nya fiko fi shém ye yì ffuuke le ɛ wvú selle.
Nyo' ɛ kume wvú yî mwɛɛm mwew mvù befe le.
Ben bò nu woŋ Nyo' le, ben elaŋlaŋè finɛn yî fiɛɛ fì kooy fô wvú le. Ben bocii bò ɛ̀ nu bonyii bo Nyo' le bô boom bo ntum e bo Jisos e noo bonyii bo ntum Nyo' le bocii, elaŋlaŋè njefo Nyo' nu ɛ sumtɛn wase nsaw yî fiɛɛ fì wvú ge bô ben e!”
yuule lawkene wvú ɛ tfume.”
Ɛ me nɛ n'yɛn wase ɛ ɛ̀ nu ɛbulɛ ke kefɛ bô nshɛ yi fiɛ le, njefo ɛbulɛ ke keyvuum bô nshɛ yi yvum to nu ɛ la wase, ɛ joo yi baay tɛn yaa bɛɛ kɛ.
Bó nu ke eyɛne bvushiw bwew e, ɛ diee diew nu ke enu ɛ bó ɛ saŋ fojise fo bó.
